```{r}
library(magrittr)

qual2 <- data.frame(category = c("Clinic", "Community"),
                    slices = c(170, 266))

qual2 %>%
  mutate(pct = round(slices / sum(slices) * 100)) %>%
  mutate(labels = paste(category, pct, "%", sep = " ")) %>%
  with({
    pie(slices, labels = labels, col = rainbow(length(labels)),
        main = "Clinic/Community")
  })
```
